[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAn AddressSanitizer heap-buffer-overflow was detected when running a [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlibFuzzer-based test on the Mongoose TCP/IP stack. The overflow occurs in the [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfunction `rx_icmp` in `net_builtin.c` at line [0m[1;36m385[0m[39m, where a single-byte read is [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mperformed just past the end of a heap-allocated buffer. The issue is triggered by a[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfuzzing input fed through the harness in `fuzz.c`.[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Issue  [0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  During fuzz testing, an `AddressSanitizer: heap-buffer-overflow` error was [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreported. The crash happens while processing an ICMP packet in the built-in network[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbackend, specifically in the function:[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;35mrx_icmp[0m[1;39m([0m[39mmg_tcpip_if*, pkt*[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m at net_builtin.[0m[1;92mc:385:18[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Vulnerability Type  [0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  The sanitizer output classifies this as a heap-buffer-overflow: a one-byte read [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mjust beyond the allocated region.[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Key Observations  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The fuzzer allocates a buffer in `LLVMFuzzerTestOneInput` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mfuzz.[0m[1;92mc:95[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpasses it to the TCP/IP receive routine [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`mg_tcpip_rx`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • In `rx_icmp`, code attempts to read packet payload beyond the buffer’s bounds [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39maccess at offset [0m[1;36m0x172[0m[39m for a [0m[1;36m34[0m[39m-byte allocation[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The call stack is: LLVMFuzzerTestOneInput → mg_tcpip_rx → rx_icmp → … → main [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mlibFuzzer[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • AddressSanitizer shadow memory shows the offending read at the first byte of [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe heap redzone.[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Important Findings  [0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The faulty read index corresponds exactly to the buffer’s length, indicating an[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moff-by-one or insufficient bounds check.  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The packet descriptor [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`pkt*`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and its length field should be examined to see [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mhow length is validated before accessing payload.  [0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The error is reproducible under the interactive libFuzzer invocation: [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`run_fuzzer fuzz -[0m[33mruns[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m100[0m[39m [0m[35m/[0m[95mtestcase[0m[39m`.[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Code Areas for Investigation  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. `src/mongoose/src/net_builtin.c` around the `rx_icmp` implementation [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline [0m[1;36m385[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand surrounding packet-parsing logic[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. The higher-level receive routine `mg_tcpip_rx` in the same file to understand [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mhow packet buffers and lengths are set up.  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. The fuzzing harness in `src/mongoose/test/fuzz.c`, particularly allocation and[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minitialization of `pkt` and any length fields, to ensure consistency between input [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msize and buffer size.  [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. Any structures or macros that define maximum ICMP packet sizes or header [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moffsets to verify proper boundary enforcement.[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m==[0m[1;36m18[0m[39m==ABORTING[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msubprocess command returned a non-zero exit status: [0m[1;36m1[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mINFO:__main__:Running: docker run --privileged --shm-[0m[33msize[0m[39m=[0m[35m2g[0m[39m --platform linux/amd64[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m--rm -i -e [0m[33mHELPER[0m[39m=[0m[3;92mTrue[0m[39m -e [0m[33mARCHITECTURE[0m[39m=[0m[35mx86_64[0m[39m -v [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/home/user/aixcc/crete/packages/python_oss_fuzz/.oss_fuzz/build/out/[0m[95mmongoose[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[95mout[0m[39m [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-v [0m[35m/tmp/[0m[95mtmp8lji3kbb[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[95mtestcase[0m[39m -t ghcr.io/aixcc-finals/base-runner:v1.[0m[1;36m3.0[0m[39m reproduce [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfuzz -[0m[33mruns[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m100[0m[39m.[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe initial issue is an AddressSanitizer-detected heap-buffer-overflow in the [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfunction `rx_icmp` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlocated in `src/net_builtin.c` at line [0m[1;36m385[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. A specially [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcrafted input fed to the fuzz harness triggered a one-byte read beyond an allocated[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpacket buffer. The provided patch attempt modifies `rx_icmp` by introducing a check[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mon the raw packet length [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`pkt->raw.len`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, computes a safe maximum payload [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`maxpay`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, and clamps the copy size accordingly. After rebuilding with this patch [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand rerunning the fuzzer, the same heap-buffer-overflow occurs at the same location[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min `rx_icmp`, indicating that the overflow was not fully prevented by the added [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlength checks.[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Initial Issue[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- A fuzz test drives `LLVMFuzzerTestOneInput`, which calls into the TCP/IP stack [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mimplementation in `net_builtin.c`.[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- During execution of `rx_icmp`, AddressSanitizer reports:[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - **READ of size [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m** at address `[0m[1;36m0x504000000172[0m[39m`[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - This address is immediately after a [0m[1;36m34[0m[39m-byte heap region [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0x504000000150[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m0x504000000172[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, meaning the code reads one byte past an [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mallocated buffer.[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - The overflow occurs at line [0m[1;36m385[0m[39m in `rx_icmp`, which handles ICMP echo requests [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mtype [0m[1;36m8[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - The stack trace shows the call sequence: `rx_icmp` → `mg_tcpip_rx` → [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`LLVMFuzzerTestOneInput` → libFuzzer internals → `main`.[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mKey observations:[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - The bug is in `rx_icmp`, specifically when copying the payload [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`pkt->pay.buf`[0m[1;39m)[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minto the transmit packet.[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - The size used for `malloc` is controlled by the fuzzer’s test harness [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`LLVMFuzzerTestOneInput`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, which allocates a buffer of size derived from the input[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlength.[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - No prior validation ensures that `pkt->pay.len` does not exceed the actual [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mallocated buffer [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`pkt->raw.len`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Patch Attempt[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe attempted patch changes `rx_icmp` as follows:[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. Adds a check:[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```c[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     size_t rawlen = pkt->raw.len;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mrawlen < hlen[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m return;[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     to abort early when the total packet length is smaller than the minimum header[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlength.[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. Defines:[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```c[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     size_t maxpay = rawlen - hlen;[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     size_t space  = ifp->tx.len - hlen;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     size_t plen   = pkt->pay.len;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mplen > maxpay[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m plen = maxpay;[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mplen > space[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  plen = space;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     to clamp the ICMP payload length to the smaller of:[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     - Remaining bytes after headers in the received packet [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`maxpay`[0m[1;39m)[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     - Remaining space in the transmit buffer [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`space`[0m[1;39m)[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch context [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m379[0m[39m in `src/net_builtin.c`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```diff[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-static void [0m[1;35mrx_icmp[0m[1;39m([0m[39mstruct mg_tcpip_if *ifp, struct pkt *pkt[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-  if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpkt->icmp->type == [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m && pkt->ip != NULL && pkt->ip->dst == ifp->ip[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-    size_t hlen = [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mstruct eth[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m + [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mstruct ip[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m + [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mstruct icmp[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-    size_t space = ifp->tx.len - hlen, plen = pkt->pay.len;[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mplen > space[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m plen = space;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-    struct ip *ip = [0m[1;35mtx_ip[0m[1;39m([0m[39mifp, pkt->eth->src, [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m, ifp->ip, pkt->ip->src,[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-                          [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mstruct icmp[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m + plen[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+static void [0m[1;35mrx_icmp[0m[1;39m([0m[39mstruct mg_tcpip_if *ifp, struct pkt *pkt[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+  if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpkt->icmp->type == [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m && pkt->ip != NULL && pkt->ip->dst == ifp->ip[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+    size_t hlen   = [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mstruct eth[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m + [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mstruct ip[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m + [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mstruct icmp[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+    size_t rawlen = pkt->raw.len;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mrawlen < hlen[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m return;[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+    size_t maxpay = rawlen - hlen;[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+    size_t space  = ifp->tx.len - hlen;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+    size_t plen   = pkt->pay.len;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mplen > maxpay[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m plen = maxpay;[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mplen > space[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  plen = space;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+    struct ip *ip = [0m[1;35mtx_ip[0m[1;39m([0m[39mifp, pkt->eth->src, [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m, ifp->ip, pkt->ip->src,[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+                          [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mstruct icmp[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m + plen[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Patch Result[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAfter rebuilding and rerunning the fuzzer, AddressSanitizer reports the same [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moverflow:[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Location**: `rx_icmp` at `net_builtin.[0m[1;92mc:385:18[0m[39m`[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Same address**: `[0m[1;36m0x504000000172[0m[39m` just beyond a [0m[1;36m34[0m[39m-byte allocation.[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Same call stack** leading back to `LLVMFuzzerTestOneInput`.[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The new checks did not prevent reading past the end of `pkt->pay.buf`.[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Areas for Further Investigation[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mTo obtain a holistic understanding of the root causes and data flow that leads to [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthis overflow, the following areas should be examined:[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Packet Buffer Allocation and Layout**  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - How `pkt->raw.len`, `pkt->pay.len`, and `pkt->pay.buf` are initialized in the [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparsing logic [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlikely in `mg_tcpip_rx` or a predecessor[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Relationship between raw packet bytes [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`pkt->raw.buf`[0m[35m/[0m[39m`.len`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and structured [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfields [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`pkt->pay.buf`[0m[35m/[0m[39m`.len`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Structure Definitions**  [0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The definitions of `struct pkt`, `struct raw`, `struct pay`, and their buffer [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpointers/sizes.[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Any implicit assumptions about contiguous memory or header sizes.[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Other Protocol Handlers**  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Similar code for TCP, UDP, or other ICMP types in `net_builtin.c` that may [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mperform unguarded copies.[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Consistency of bounds checking across different packet handlers.[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Transmit Buffer [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`ifp->tx`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Management**  [0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - How `ifp->tx.len` is determined and whether it always represents the actual [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcapacity of `ifp->tx.buf`.[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Fuzzer Harness and Test Inputs**  [0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - How the fuzzing harness constructs `pkt` and whether it can produce [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcontradictory length fields [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`raw.len` smaller than headers but `pay.len` nonzero[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Validity checks [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor lack thereof[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m in `LLVMFuzzerTestOneInput` before passing [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdata into the stack.[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mBy tracing the packet through its parsing, header extraction, and payload buffering[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mphases, one can identify the exact mismatch between declared lengths and actual [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbuffers that permits a read past the end of `pkt->pay.buf`. This will guide further[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfixes and consistent boundary enforcement.[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Initial Issue Log[0m                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAn AddressSanitizer report shows a heap-buffer-overflow in `rx_icmp` [0m[1;39m([0m[39min [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`src/net_builtin.c` at line [0m[1;36m385[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, triggered by an LLVM-libfuzzer harness. The patch[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mattempt modifies `[0m[1;35mmkpay[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`—the function that sets `pkt->pay`—to more conservatively[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcompute payload length, replacing the original pointer-difference calculation with [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39ma clamped “available bytes” approach. After applying the patch, the same overflow [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min `rx_icmp` persists under fuzzing, indicating that the change to `[0m[1;35mmkpay[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` did [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnot prevent the out-of-bounds read in `rx_icmp`.[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mInitial Issue  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The fuzzer harness calls `LLVMFuzzerTestOneInput`, which allocates a `pkt` [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstructure and invokes network-processing functions in Mongoose.  [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- In `[0m[1;35mrx_icmp[0m[1;39m([0m[39mmg_tcpip_if*, pkt*[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, a one-byte read occurs just past the end of a [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mheap buffer:  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - Address [0m[1;36m0x504000000172[0m[39m is immediately after a [0m[1;36m34[0m[39m-byte region [0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0x[0m[39m…[0m[1;36m150[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m0x[0m[39m…[0m[1;36m172[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - The crash stack trace identifies line [0m[1;36m385[0m[39m of `src/net_builtin.c` inside [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`rx_icmp` as the read site.  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - The input is supplied by fuzzing code at `mongoose/test/fuzz.[0m[1;92mc:106[0m[39m`.[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mKey Observations in Initial Log  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The overflow is reproducible on every run with different seeds.  [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The corrupted read is in the ICMP handler, not in fuzzer initialization or [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mharness code.  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The heap allocation of size [0m[1;36m34[0m[39m bytes happens in `LLVMFuzzerTestOneInput` before [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpassing the buffer to TCP/IP routines.  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The overflow is consistently a [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m-byte read just past the allocated region.[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch Attempt  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Function `[0m[1;35mmkpay[0m[1;39m([0m[39mstruct pkt *pkt, void *p[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` was modified. Original code:  [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    pkt->pay = [0m[1;35mmg_str_n[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mchar *[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mp, [0m[1;39m([0m[39m&pkt->raw.buf[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mpkt->raw.len[0m[1;39m][0m[39m - [0m[1;39m([0m[39mchar *[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mp[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- New code:  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    • Compute `offset = p – pkt->raw.buf`  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    • If `pkt->raw.len > offset`, set `avail = pkt->raw.len - offset`; else `avail [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m= [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m`  [0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    • Call `[0m[1;35mmg_str_n[0m[1;39m([0m[39mp, avail[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The change bounds the payload length to the remaining bytes in `pkt->raw.buf`.  [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mLog After Patch  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Fuzzer run again under AddressSanitizer.  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Same stack trace and same buffer bounds violation in `rx_icmp` at the same [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39maddress.  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The patch to `[0m[1;35mmkpay[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` did not affect the overflow in `rx_icmp`.[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAreas for Further Investigation  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The body of `rx_icmp` around line [0m[1;36m385[0m[39m: array indexing or pointer arithmetic that [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreads beyond `pkt->raw.buf`.  [0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- How `pkt->raw.len` and `pkt->raw.buf` are initialized and whether their [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrelationship to actual buffer size is guaranteed.  [0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Any upstream parsing or validation of the ICMP packet length fields.  [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Interactions between `[0m[1;35mmkpay[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and other packet-processing functions [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., IP [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mheader parsing, `mg_tcpip_rx`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Potential mismatches between allocated buffer size in the fuzz harness and [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexpected minimum packet sizes in `rx_icmp`.[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Initial Issue Log[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mHere is the initial issue log of the codebase:[0m                                      [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  Container overflow:      fc[0m                                                       [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  Intra object redzone:    bb[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ASan internal:           fe[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  Left alloca redzone:     ca[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  Right alloca redzone:    cb[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m==[0m[1;36m18[0m[39m==ABORTING[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msubprocess command returned a non-zero exit status: [0m[1;36m1[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mINFO:__main__:Running: docker run --privileged --shm-[0m[33msize[0m[39m=[0m[35m2g[0m[39m --platform linux/amd64[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m--rm -i -e [0m[33mHELPER[0m[39m=[0m[3;92mTrue[0m[39m -e [0m[33mARCHITECTURE[0m[39m=[0m[35mx86_64[0m[39m -v [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/home/user/aixcc/crete/packages/python_oss_fuzz/.oss_fuzz/build/out/[0m[95mmongoose[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[95mout[0m[39m [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-v [0m[35m/tmp/[0m[95mtmp8lji3kbb[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[95mtestcase[0m[39m -t ghcr.io/aixcc-finals/base-runner:v1.[0m[1;36m3.0[0m[39m reproduce [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfuzz -[0m[33mruns[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m100[0m[39m.[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAn AddressSanitizer report revealed a heap-buffer-overflow in the function [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`rx_icmp` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnet_builtin.[0m[1;92mc:385[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m when the fuzzer invoked `mg_tcpip_rx`. The overflow [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moccurs on a one‐byte read just past a [0m[1;36m34[0m[39m‐byte heap allocation, reading [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`pkt->icmp->type`. A tentative patch was applied:  [0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- In `mkpay`, the computation of the payload length was revised to clamp to [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mremaining bytes.  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- In `rx_icmp`, a guard was added to return early if the ICMP header does not fully[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfit within `pkt->raw.buf + pkt->raw.len`.  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mHowever, after applying this patch, the same heap‐buffer‐overflow recurred under [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfuzzing in `rx_icmp` at the same location and with the same memory bounds.[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Initial Issue**  [0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The fuzzer ran `LLVMFuzzerTestOneInput`, which calls into `mg_tcpip_rx`, [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39meventually leading to `[0m[1;35mrx_icmp[0m[1;39m([0m[39mifp, pkt[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - AddressSanitizer flagged a [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m‐byte read at address `[0m[1;36m0x504000000172[0m[39m`, which is [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mimmediately past the end of a [0m[1;36m34[0m[39m‐byte region [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0x504000000150[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m0x504000000172[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mallocated by `malloc`.  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The offending instruction is reading `pkt->icmp->type`, attempting to read an [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mICMP header that extends beyond the received packet buffer.  [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Stack trace levels:  [0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. rx_icmp [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnet_builtin.[0m[1;92mc:385[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. mg_tcpip_rx [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnet_builtin.[0m[1;92mc:897[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. LLVMFuzzerTestOneInput [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtest/fuzz.[0m[1;92mc:106[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. Fuzzer driver internals  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Important Observations**  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The packet buffer [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`pkt->raw.buf`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is smaller than the expected size of the [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mICMP header.  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The read happens unconditionally on every ICMP packet type check [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`pkt->icmp->type == [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The allocation size [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m34[0m[39m bytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m suggests that only partial headers or malformed[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minputs are being fuzzed.  [0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Patch Attempt**  [0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In `[0m[1;35mmkpay[0m[1;39m([0m[39mstruct pkt *pkt, void *p[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`:  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```c[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       char *start = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mchar *[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mp;[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       size_t offset = [0m[1;39m([0m[39msize_t[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m([0m[39mstart - [0m[1;39m([0m[39mchar *[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mpkt->raw.buf[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       size_t avail = pkt->raw.len > offset ? pkt->raw.len - offset : [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       pkt->pay = [0m[1;35mmg_str_n[0m[1;39m([0m[39mstart, avail[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     This change limits the computed payload `pkt->pay` to the remaining buffer [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlength.  [0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In `[0m[1;35mrx_icmp[0m[1;39m([0m[39mstruct mg_tcpip_if *ifp, struct pkt *pkt[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`:  [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```c[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mchar *[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mpkt->icmp + [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39m*pkt->icmp[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m >[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[1;39m([0m[39mchar *[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mpkt->raw.buf + pkt->raw.len[0m[1;39m)[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         return;[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     This guard was added to bail out when the ICMP header would overrun the packet[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbuffer.  [0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Result After Patch**  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Upon rerunning the fuzzer for [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m iterations, AddressSanitizer reports the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msame heap-buffer-overflow at net_builtin.[0m[1;92mc:385[0m[39m inside `rx_icmp`.  [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The allocation, read address, and stack trace are identical to the original [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfailure.  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The boundary check did not prevent the out‐of‐bounds read in this test case, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mindicating the check condition did not match the fuzzed input scenario.[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Areas for Further Investigation**  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **pkt->icmp Pointer Initialization:** Review how `pkt->icmp` is derived from [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`pkt->raw.buf` [0m[1;39m([0m[39moffsets, alignment, parsing[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Packet Length Fields:** Verify lengths stored in `pkt->raw.len` and any [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mintermediate header-length calculations.  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Header Parsing Logic in mg_tcpip_rx:** Check IP header processing that sets [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`pkt->icmp`, including any assumptions about header presence and contiguous layout.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **mkpay Interaction:** Though the overflow is in `rx_icmp`, reassess whether [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mincorrect payload bounds in `mkpay` lead to corrupted state that affects ICMP [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparsing.  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Edge Cases in Fuzz Harness:** Ensure that the fuzzed inputs are interpreted [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcorrectly by the parsing routines and that no intermediate casts or pointer [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39marithmetic is invalid.[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Initial Issue Log[0m                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwithin `src/net_builtin.c`. An attempt to mitigate the issue by adding a bounds [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcheck around the `pkt->icmp` pointer did not prevent the crash: after applying the [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpatch, AddressSanitizer still reports the same overflow at the same source line. [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe issue persists and requires further investigation in how packet data, buffer [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlength and the ICMP header pointer are managed.[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mInitial Issue  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- A libFuzzer run with AddressSanitizer triggered a heap-buffer-overflow in [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mrx_icmp[0m[1;39m([0m[39mmg_tcpip_if*, pkt*[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` at `net_builtin.[0m[1;92mc:385:18[0m[39m`.  [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The crash occurs on a [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m-byte read just beyond a [0m[1;36m34[0m[39m-byte allocated region [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0x[0m[33m...[0m[1;36m150[0m[39m, [0m[1;36m0x[0m[33m...[0m[1;36m172[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Call stack highlights that `rx_icmp` is invoked by `mg_tcpip_rx`, which in turn [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mis driven by `LLVMFuzzerTestOneInput` in the fuzz harness.  [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mKey Observations  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The overflow address [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`[0m[1;36m0x[0m[33m...[0m[1;36m172[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is exactly one byte past the end of the buffer [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msegment [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`raw.buf + raw.len`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The heap allocation happens in the fuzzer entry point [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`LLVMFuzzerTestOneInput`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhich allocates `pkt->raw.buf` and sets `pkt->raw.len`.  [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- No other sanitizer notes [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g. UAF or double free[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m accompany the report—this is a[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstraightforward out-of-bounds read.  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch Attempt  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Location: around line [0m[1;36m381[0m[39m of `src/net_builtin.c`, within the `static void [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mrx_icmp[0m[1;39m([0m[39mstruct mg_tcpip_if *ifp, struct pkt *pkt[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` function.  [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Inserted code:[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    ```[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mchar *[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mpkt->icmp < [0m[1;39m([0m[39mchar *[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mpkt->raw.buf ||[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m([0m[39mchar *[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mpkt->icmp + [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39m*pkt->icmp[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m > [0m[1;39m([0m[39mchar *[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mpkt->raw.buf + [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpkt->raw.len[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      return;[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    ```[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  This check was intended to exit early when the ICMP header would be out of the [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mraw buffer bounds.  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The rest of the function remains unchanged; in particular, subsequent logic [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mchecks `pkt->icmp->type` and payload handling.  [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mResult After Patch  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- A subsequent fuzz iteration produced an identical AddressSanitizer report at [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`net_builtin.[0m[1;92mc:385:18[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi.e. inside the same bounds check context[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, confirming the [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moverflow still occurs.  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- All log details—heap allocation, shadow bytes legend, call stack—match the [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minitial failure, indicating the guard did not catch the problematic case.  [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAreas for Further Investigation  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Construction and initialization of `pkt->raw.buf` and `pkt->raw.len` in the [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpacket parsing logic. Ensure these fields accurately reflect the actual buffer [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msize.  [0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Assignment of `pkt->icmp` pointer: verify that it points to a location within the[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbuffer [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g. packet parsing routines that set `icmp` based on header offsets[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Header size calculations [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`[0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mstruct eth[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, `[0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mstruct ip[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mstruct icmp[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and how they relate to `raw.len`—any mismatches or missing [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mchecks may lead to under-sized buffers.  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Code in `mg_tcpip_rx` that hands off the packet to `rx_icmp`, to trace how [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmalformed or truncated packets could reach this function.  [0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Fuzz harness [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`fuzz.c`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m usage of packet structure allocation and content [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minjection, to ensure packet members are initialized in a way that triggers valid [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mboundary checks.[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
